{"tid":610933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞人油麻地劏房內「打邊爐」致火警","createTime":"2018-03-30T12:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T18:27:20.000Z","uid":42188,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"768f917ce87336121dd9bef199dfc9c4b376293a","tid":610933,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"[因涉嫌販運700噸白粉原材料而被政府檢控，繼而棄保潛逃到台灣成為本港頭號通緝犯，亦使自己終身未能返港，及後多次哀求政府撤銷通緝令不果，最終客死異鄉並經常被網民恥笑的東方日報創辦人馬惜珍，其所創辦的東方日報報道] 油麻地發生劏房火警。傍晚6時許，上海街與熙龍里交界1樓一個劏房單位，突然起火冒煙，多名街坊見狀報警。現場火勢猛烈伴隨滾滾濃煙，令一帶天台位置煙霧瀰漫。消防員接報趕抵，架起2條雲梯開喉灌救，並將窗户玻璃打碎散熱。<br />\n<br />\n火勢至晚上6時44分救熄，無人受傷。該幢唐樓5層高，1樓滿布劏房，現場消息指，事發時有南亞人在劏房內「打邊爐」，疑不慎引起火警。3名南亞男女其後在場接受救護員檢查。 <br />\n<br />\n受火警影響，附近交通受阻，窩打老道現時不能左轉入上海街。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180330/mobile/bkn-20180330184014157-0330_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180330%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180330184014157-0330_00822_001.html&d=5uhCr9pl1eHD9o0NWXfhUQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3fbe4f5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180330/mobile/bkn-20180330184014157-0330_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"faa11361a864f82065af4a12f5a13865fefbe06b","tid":610933,"uid":115354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"啲蝻真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff562e184ff452151383fd0bcefee3ca1a8caff","tid":610933,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a4d706d7935cc587bb9d272aade94f5f8f2945","tid":610933,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e72a90b21bf2f5e609904a11d67d6f0e6527606b","tid":610933,"u